00069 void GenericFileReaderTest::testmethod_ReadHeaderMinDP_when_file_exists()
00070 {
00071         GenericData data;
00072         GenericFileReader reader;
00073         std::string name = TEST_DATA_DAT_FILE;
00074         reader.SetFilename(name);
00075         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_NO_THROW(reader.ReadHeader(data, GenericFileReader::ReadMinDataGroupHeader));
00076         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data.Header().GetFilename() == TEST_DATA_DAT_FILE);
00077 
00078         Check_TEST_DATA_DAT_FILE_GenericHeader(data);
00079 
00080         // Check the DataGroupHeader information.
00081         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data.Header().GetDataGroupCnt() == 1);
00082         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data.Header().GetNumDataGroups() == 1);
00083 
00084         DataGroupHdrIt dchBegin, dchEnd;
00085         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_NO_THROW(data.Header().GetDataGroupIts(dchBegin, dchEnd));
00086         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(dchBegin->GetName() == L"First Data Cube");
00087         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(dchBegin->GetDataSetCnt() == 1);
00088         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(dchBegin->GetDataSetPos() == 0x2d1);
00089         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(dchBegin->GetNextGroupPos() == 0x468);
00090 
00091         // Check that the minimum DataSetHeader information was read.
00092         DataSetHdrIt dphBegin, dphEnd;
00093         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_NO_THROW(dchBegin->GetDataSetIterators(dphBegin,dphEnd));
00094         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(dphBegin->GetName() == L"acquired data");
00095         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(dphBegin->GetDataStartFilePos() != 0);
00096         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(dphBegin->GetNameValParamCnt() == 0);
00097         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(dphBegin->GetRowSize() == 0);
00098         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(dphBegin->GetDataSize() == 0);
00099         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(dphBegin->GetRowCnt() == 0);
00100         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(dphBegin->GetColumnCnt() == 0);
00101         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(dphBegin->GetDataStartFilePos() == 0x3A0);
00102 
00103         // Check that there are not any more DataSetHeaders
00104         ++dphBegin;
00105         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(dphBegin == dphEnd);
00106 
00107         // Check that there are not any more DataGroupHeaders
00108         ++dchBegin;
00109         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(dchBegin == dchEnd);

00226 void GenericFileReaderTest::Check_TEST_DATA_DAT_FILE_GenericHeader(GenericData& data)
00227 {
00228         // Check the file generic header
00229         GenericDataHeader* gdh = data.Header().GetGenericDataHdr();
00230         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gdh->GetFileTypeId() == SCAN_ACQUISITION_DATA_TYPE);
00231         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gdh->GetFileId() == "test-dat-guid");
00232         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data.FileIdentifier() == "test-dat-guid");
00233         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gdh->GetFileCreationTime() == L"2004-07-04T11:12:13Z");
00234         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gdh->GetLocale() == L"en-US");
00235 
00236         ParameterNameValueTypeIt nvpBegin, nvpEnd;
00237         gdh->GetNameValIterators(nvpBegin, nvpEnd);
00238         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvpBegin != nvpEnd);
00239         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvpBegin->GetName() == ARRAY_TYPE_PARAM_NAME);
00240         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvpBegin->GetValueText() == L"Hg-U133A");
00241         ++nvpBegin;
00242         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvpBegin != nvpEnd);
00243         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvpBegin->GetName() == ARRAY_BARCODE_PARAM_NAME);
00244         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvpBegin->GetValueText() == L"Barcode");
00245         ++nvpBegin;
00246         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvpBegin != nvpEnd);
00247         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvpBegin->GetName() == L"Parameter1");
00248         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvpBegin->GetValueText() == L"Value1");
00249         ++nvpBegin;
00250         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvpBegin == nvpEnd);
00251 
00252         // Check the parent header 
00253         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gdh->GetParentCnt() == 1);
00254         GenDataHdrVectorIt parentBegin, parentEnd;
00255         gdh->GetParentIterators(parentBegin, parentEnd);
00256         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(parentBegin != parentEnd);
00257         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(parentBegin->GetFileTypeId() == ARRAY_TYPE_IDENTIFIER);
00258         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(parentBegin->GetFileId() == "test-array-guid");
00259         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data.ArrayFileIdentifier() == "test-array-guid");
00260         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(parentBegin->GetFileCreationTime() == L"2004-07-01T13:14:15Z");
00261         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(parentBegin->GetLocale() == L"en-US");
00262         
00263         parentBegin->GetNameValIterators(nvpBegin, nvpEnd);
00264         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvpBegin != nvpEnd);
00265         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvpBegin->GetName() == ARRAY_TYPE_PARAM_NAME);
00266         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvpBegin->GetValueText() == L"Hg-U133A");
00267         ++nvpBegin;
00268         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvpBegin != nvpEnd);
00269         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvpBegin->GetName() == ARRAY_LOT_PARAM_NAME);
00270         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvpBegin->GetValueText() == L"Thanks alot");
00271         ++nvpBegin;
00272         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvpBegin == nvpEnd);
00273 
00274         ++parentBegin;
00275         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(parentBegin == parentEnd);
00276 }

00387

00391                 std::wstring expectedName;

00393                         expectedName = L"Probe Set Names";

00395                 {
00396                         FormatString1(name, 100, L"biob_%d", i-1);
00397                         expectedName = name;
00398                 }
00399 
00400                 CPPUNIT_ASSERT(names[i] == expectedName);
00401         }

00404 void GenericFileReaderTest::ReadHeaderOfFileWithReserveStringParameters()
00405 {
00406         GenericData data;
00407         GenericFileReader reader;
00408         reader.SetFilename("../data/small_dat_file_with_reserved_string_parameters");
00409         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_NO_THROW(reader.ReadHeader(data, GenericFileReader::ReadAllHeaders));
00410 
00411         // Check array id because it has reserved space and is stored as an ASCII string.
00412         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data.ArrayIdentifier() == "smellsliketeenspirit");
00413 
00414         // Get the raw parameter to check the length.
00415         bool found = false;
00416         int32_t parentHeaderCount = data.Header().GetGenericDataHdr()->GetParentCnt();
00417         for (int32_t index = 0; index < parentHeaderCount; ++index)
00418         {
00419                 GenericDataHeader genericHdr = data.Header().GetGenericDataHdr()->GetParent(index);
00420                 if (genericHdr.GetFileTypeId() == ARRAY_TYPE_IDENTIFIER)
00421                 {
00422                         ParameterNameValueType nvt;
00423                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(genericHdr.FindNameValParam(ARRAY_ID_PARAM_NAME, nvt));
00424                         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(nvt.GetMIMEValue().Size() == AFFY_GUID_LEN);
00425                         found = true;
00426                         break;
00427                 }
00428         }
00429 
00430         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(found);
00431 
00432         // Check reserved wchar string.
00433         ParameterNameValueType result;
00434         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data.Header().GetGenericDataHdr()->FindNameValParam(L"fixedlen", result));
00435         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(result.GetValueText() == L"twenty-five");
00436         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(result.GetMIMEValue().Size() == 25*sizeof(u_int16_t));
00437 }
